SUMMARY:Servant Stage Company’s A BROADWAY MELODY
DESCRIPTION:Step into the spotlight with A Broadway Melody! This spectacular revue celebrates 100 years of Broadway magic\, featuring unforgettable songs and showstoppers from the greatest musicals of all time. With a powerhouse cast of dynamic performers\, this intimate cabaret-style performance brings the best of the Great White Way up close and personal. From classic tunes to modern hits\, A Broadway Melody is a joyful\, high-energy tribute to the music\, memories\, and magic that have defined a century of Broadway!
