SUMMARY:St. Baldrick's Fundraiser
DESCRIPTION:Since 2008\, the head-shaving extravaganza hosted at Annie Bailey’s Irish Public House has raised over $1 MILLION in support of the St. Baldrick’s Foundation’s ongoing fight to end childhood cancers. Whether you decide to #bravetheshave yourself\, volunteer your hair-cutting services as a shaver\, or support by making a donation\, we hope you’ll join us in helping to give hope to infants\, children\, teens & young adults fighting cancer! \n\n\n\nShaving starts at 12pm and ends at 3pm\, don’t miss your opportunity to support!
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/st-baldricks-fundraiser/
LOCATION:Annie Bailey’s Irish Pub & Restaurant\, 28-30 East King Street\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17602\, United States
CATEGORIES:Community Events,Free Events and Activites
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/470A3677-1.jpeg
