SUMMARY:Saturday Night Improv: Indie Mixtape
DESCRIPTION:Independent improv teams mix it up on the Lancaster Improv Players’ stage! \n\n\n\nAn evening of chuckles\, giggles\, guffaws\, and snorts provided by local indie teams! \n\n\n\nBut you may be asking. . . what is an “indie team”? \n\n\n\nAn indie team is an improv team that forms outside of the traditional means; sometimes they start as practice or study groups\, and sometimes they are formed around specific ideas or formats. Typically\, the terminology is used to differentiate from a ‘house team’\, which is a team started through an improv theater. \n\n\n\nFEATURING: Hippie & Frenchie and Glorzebub! \n\n\n\nBYOB \n\n\n\n$15 at the door \n\n\n\nDue to the size of our theater\, there is a quick turnover time between our scheduled shows. If you purchase tickets to both events on Saturday evening\, you will be asked to wait outside during the break so that the next team can warm up before the audience returns.
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/saturday-night-improv-indie-mixtape-3/
LOCATION:The Lancaster Improv Theater\, 16 S Prince Str\, Lancaster\, Pennsylvania\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Theatre
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/indie-mix-tape-1.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Lancaster Improv Players":MAILTO:kate@lancasterimprovplayers.org
END:VEVENT
