SUMMARY:Wowtown Vintage Retro Dance Party
DESCRIPTION:Get ready to move\, groove\, and lose yourself in the best sounds of the past and present. Wowtown is bringing the heat with a full night of vintage and retro dance floor fire\, no filters\, no gimmicks\, just pure party energy from start to finish. \n\n\n\nBehind the Decks: DJ XCJSpinning a wild ride through Motown\, R&B\, Surf\, Disco\, House\, and pure Party Chaos. Every era\, every vibe\, all night long. \n\n\n\nLive Performances: Go-Go & Pole ArtistryThree electrifying performers — Yaz\, Faceless\, and Della Arte — bring the stage to life with live go-go and pole artistry that’ll keep your eyes as busy as your feet. \n\n\n\nFull BarCold beers\, handcrafted cocktails\, mocktails\, and infused beverages available all night. Drink up and dance harder. \n\n\n\nTICKETS$10 · Advance$15 · At the Door (Save a few bucks — grab yours early.) \n\n\n\nCLICK TO BUY TICKETS LINK \n\n\n\n⚠ 21+ EVENT · VALID ID REQUIRED
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/wowtown-vintage-retro-dance-party-2/
LOCATION:The Lounge at Hempfield Apothetique\, 100 W Walnut St\, Lancaster\, Pennsylvania\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Music and Dance
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/cityoflancasterpa-242134369851055-6503474183366449790-45-6.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Hempfield Apothetique":MAILTO:hello@HempfieldApothetique.com
END:VEVENT
