SUMMARY:Live Model Figure Drawing at Lancaster Art Vault
DESCRIPTION:Sessions are held the2nd Tuesday of every month from 6-9PM. Registration RequiredJoin Lancaster Art Vault for a Figure Drawing session with a live model for beginner and experienced artists (Adults 18+ only). Next Session: April 14 and May 12 \n\n\n\nSessions are uninstructed & artists must bring their own drawing/painting supplies. Tables and easels are available. \n\n\n\nEach session is 3 hours and costs $20. Sign-ups and payment can be made at LancasterArtVault.com.  Lancaster Art Vault is located at 100 North Queen Street\, Lancaster.Email Info@LancasterArtVault.com for more information.
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/live-model-figure-drawing-at-lancaster-art-vault/
LOCATION:Lancaster Art Vault\, 100 North Queen Street\, 1st Floor\, Lancaster\, Pennsylvania\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Arts and Culture,Classes and Workshops
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/Figure-Drawing.jpg
