SUMMARY:Latin Dance Night At West Art
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Salsa & Bachata lessons from Luis Santiago\, and then DJ Rumspringa will bring back his high-energy mix designed to keep the floor moving all night long. No experience? Perfect. Been waiting for a sign to try Latin dance? This is your sign to do it. Bring a friend\, bring your hips\, let’s make the room move!Latin Dance Socials will be held on the 2nd Tuesday of the month. \n\n\n\nWhat to expect at the show:>> Doors will open at 7:00.>> Tickets are $10 in advance and at the door if not sold out. As always\, we’re proud to present an all-ages event!>> Parking is available on the street around F&M College. We suggest finding a spot on the park side of Buchanan Ave\, Race Ave\, or College Ave (North of Buchanan). Thank you for helping us be good neighbors!>> Format: This will be a standing event in City Hall. Our space is ADA accessible\, and we will do our best to accommodate any specific needs.>> If you haven’t yet discovered the magic of the West Art Coffee⚡Bar\, now’s your chance! We’re open from 7 am-10 pm daily\, with a full and delicious espresso bar menu\, along with a lovely selection of beer\, wine\, and cocktails\, plenty of N/A options\, and some tasty bites from our favorite local bakeries. Something for everyone\, all day long! Come hang out before the show and experience it for yourself!>> Please note that all ticket sales are final. Tickets purchased using digital payment methods include a small service fee. Cash purchases at the door are not subject to this fee. Thank you for supporting great music!
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/latin-dance-night-at-west-art/
LOCATION:West Art Community Center\, 816 Buchanan Ave\, Lancaster\, Pennsylvania\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Music and Dance
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/cityoflancasterpa-242134369851055-6513157347714957861-westartlatindancebanner.png
ORGANIZER;CN="DJ Rumspringa":MAILTO:contact@mstoltzfus.com
END:VEVENT
