SUMMARY:Spring Is in the Air Moss Wall Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Design a framed moss wall with preserved moss\, botanicals\, and two air plants in this hands-on\, guided workshop.Unwind at the end of your day and join us for an intimate happy hour workshop with expert instruction. As always\, BYOB.Create a one-of-a-kind moss wall that brings texture\, nature\, and art together in a beautiful\, modern way.In this hands-on workshop\, you’ll design a framed moss wall using a thoughtfully curated selection of preserved moss\, dried elements\, and botanical accents. Two air plants will be incorporated into your piece\, adding sculptural dimension and a living touch to your finished design.Our very own featured moss wall artist\, Laura Alvis\, will guide you through the creative process\, offering styling tips\, composition guidance\, and design insight along the way. Whether your aesthetic leans minimal and modern or lush and layered\, you’ll have the support to make it uniquely yours.
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/spring-is-in-the-air-moss-wall-workshop/
LOCATION:Gallery Grow Plant Bar\, 320 N Queen St.\, Lancaster\, Pennsylvania\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Classes and Workshops
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/Moss-Wall-header.jpeg
ORGANIZER;CN="Gallery Grow Plant Bar":MAILTO:contact@gallerygrow.com
END:VEVENT
