SUMMARY:Backstreet Brothel Historic Walking Tour & Our Town Brewery Happy Hour
DESCRIPTION:On this history tour\, walk the streets of Lancaster with an expert guide and learn about the brothel keepers\, bartenders\, and pool hall hustlers who shared the streets with corrupt politicians and righteous reformers a century ago. \n\n\n\nAfter the tour\, enjoy a “Mini Flight and a Bite” at Our Town Brewery\, which is on the site of one of Lancaster’s elite brothels in the early 1900s. We’ll also learn about the history of Lancaster brewing and compete in Lancaster Vice Trivia. \n\n\n\nThe cost of Happy Hour at Our Town Brewery is included in the price of this special event.
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/backstreet-brothel-historic-walking-tour-our-town-brewery-happy-hour/
